title: Week 11 Picks, Tyrod Taylor Benched, Jerry Jones Warned
description:
Will Brinson, Jason La Canfora, Pete Prisco and Nick Kostos link up for the Week 11 picks pod! First, Will and Jason discuss what's going on in Buffalo with the benching of quarterback Tyrod Taylor, and the latest on Jerry Jones vs. the NFL, while getting JLC's "Satanic Voice Bet of the Week." Then, Will is joined by Pete and Nick to make their picks across the league in Week 11, including 'Andy Reid off the bye!', a 7-2 vs. 7-2 battle between the Vikings and Rams, a coaching mismatch in Pats vs. Raiders, an NFC East rivalry featuring the Eagles and Cowboys, and Monday Night clash with the Falcons in Seattle.
